31
00:01:44,200 --> 00:01:45,880
[HUMS]

32
00:01:46,320 --> 00:01:49,300
- Well, Moe.
- Homer, I'm so sorry. Have a free beer.

33
00:01:49,920 --> 00:01:51,390
Oh.

34
